headline: ISRG Shares Rise as FDA Clears AI Integration for Ion Platform
summary: Intuitive Surgical shares climb after FDA clears AI-driven upgrades for its Ion platform, boosting precision and efficiency in lung biopsies.

headline: West to Host Third-Quarter 2025 Conference Call
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), a global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that it will release third-quarter financial results before the market opens on Thursday, October 23, 2025, and will follow with a conference call to discuss the results and business expectations at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time.
